Name: pydantic
URL: https://github.com/pydantic/pydantic
Revision: 5f033e46c54fea1b59b6894d6527daf49475e690
Version: 2.11.7
License: MIT
License File: src/LICENSE
Description: Data validation using Python type hints.

The version of pydantic is generally pinned to the version that is compatible with pydantic_core,
which is provided as a Python wheel via CIPD:
https://chrome-infra-packages.appspot.com/p/infra/python/wheels/pydantic_core.

This package is pinned to a particular version in //manifests/third_party/pylibs/requirements.in and
then running //manifests/third_party/pylibs/update-pylibs.sh. pydantic_core must then also be
updated in //manifests/prebuilts to a compatible version. See
//prebuilt/third_party/pydantic-core/README.fuchsia for details about updating pydantic_core.
